Global Time-of-flight Camera Market Insights
Time-of-flight Camera Market size was valued at USD 1.38 Billion in 2022 and is projected to reach USD 4.82 Billion by 2030, growing at a CAGR of 17.9% from 2024 to 2030.

Time-of-flight Camera Market Overview
The global Time-of-flight (ToF) camera market was valued at approximately USD 2.3 billion in 2023 and is expected to reach USD 7.5 billion by 2030, growing at a CAGR of 18.5% from 2024 to 2030. This growth is driven by advancements in 3D imaging technologies, increasing demand for autonomous systems, and the integration of ToF cameras in consumer electronics, robotics, and automotive applications. With increasing adoption across sectors such as healthcare, security, and manufacturing, the market is expected to expand significantly in the coming years.

